trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged"></xref> events.
trans-unit.target: Adja meg az adatait a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged"> </xref> és <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged"> </xref> események.

trans-unit.source: The ChildChangedEventArgs class is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> classes when the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties change.
trans-unit.target: A ChildChangedEventArgs osztály által használt a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost>és <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost>osztályok mikor értékeit a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName>vagy <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName>tulajdonságainak módosítása.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A> property to get the previously assigned child control or element.
trans-unit.target: Használja a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A>tulajdonság használatával beolvassa a korábban hozzárendelt gyermekvezérlő vagy elem.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A>
